STATE of North Carolina
v.
Charles Gene ROGERS No. 444P09-6 Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 16, 2019 Charles Gene Rogers, for Rogers, Charles Gene. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 15th of April 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wayne County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th of April 2019."
